    {
        "ai_id": 1,
        "ai_name": "AI Bot 1",
        "api": "https://example.com/api/ai/1",
        "score": 95
    },
    {
        "ai_id": 2,
        "ai_name": "AI Bot 2",
        "api": "https://example.com/api/ai/2",
        "score": 88
    }
]
</code></pre> <p>所有错误响应的格式均为：</p> <pre><code>{
    "code": * ,
    "info": "[Some message]"
}
</code></pre> <p>若读取数据中途抛出错误，错误响应的状态码为 <code>500 Internal Server Error</code>，code 字段为 <code>-4</code>，info 字段尽量携带错误信息。</p>

