    "code": 0,
    "info": "AI created successfully",
    "ai_id": 3
}
</code></pre> <ul> <li><code>ai_id</code>: 新生成的 AI 的唯一标识符。</li> </ul> <p>所有错误响应的格式均为：</p> <pre><code>{
    "code": * ,
    "info": "[Some message]"
